      </div>
    
          <div class="card-inset-details__teaser-text">
        
            People are frequently using more than one drug at a time, and they&#039;re more powerful than ever. That&#039;s a deadly combination.
      
      </div>
    
  </div>

</article>      </div>
    


  
          <div class="teaser--card-inset-details--row">
    

<article class="teaser--card-inset-details blog_entry--teaser--card-inset-details" data-nid="5019121">

      <div class="card-inset-details__image">
        <a href="/us/blog/addiction-outlook/202404/genetics-and-addiction"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn2.psychologytoday.com/assets/styles/manual_crop_3_2_600x400/public/field_blog_entry_images/2024-04/iStock-164480772.jpg?itok=8NUyrmnv" width="600" height="400" alt="Human genetics" title="iStock/andrey alyukhin" />

</a>

    </div>
  
  <div class="card-inset-details__body">

          <div class="card-inset-details__title">
        <a href="/us/blog/addiction-outlook/202404/genetics-and-addiction" title="Genetics and Addiction: What We&#039;ve Learned"> Genetics and Addiction: What We&#039;ve Learned </a>
      </div>
    
          <div class="card-inset-details__teaser-text">
        
            The latest findings on genetics reveals how genes may affect the risk for substance use disorders, and how they can help predict which treatment will work.
      
      </div>
    
  </div>

</article>


  
    

<article class="teaser--card-inset-details blog_entry--teaser--card-inset-details" data-nid="5017846">

      <div class="card-inset-details__image">
      
              <a href="/us/blog/demystifying-addiction/202403/addiction-psychotherapy-and-harm-reduction-go-hand-in-hand"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn2.psychologytoday.com/assets/styles/manual_crop_3_2_600x400/public/teaser_image/blog_entry/2024-04/shutterstock_1603389958.jpg?itok=fov1DgGD" width="600" height="400" alt="" title="VH-studio/Shutterstock" />

</a>

      
    </div>
  
  <div class="card-inset-details__body">

          <div class="card-inset-details__title">
        <a href="/us/blog/demystifying-addiction/202403/addiction-psychotherapy-and-harm-reduction-go-hand-in-hand" title="Addiction Psychotherapy and Harm Reduction Go Hand In Hand"> Addiction Psychotherapy and Harm Reduction Go Hand In Hand </a>
      </div>
    
          <div class="card-inset-details__teaser-text">
        
            Our myopic view of abstinence in addiction recovery is informed by stigma and bias. There may be a better way.
      
      </div>
    
  </div>

</article>      </div>
    


  </section>

    

  
  

  
  
